{"type": "article", "id": 37098, "title": "这个相当特殊的“冰箱”，不做饭的人会喜欢｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-01-22T22:57:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 36968, "name": "Full Grown"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 157, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170123090945rGsVWh79ntI32JUy.jpg", "contents": "<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Full Grown</h3><p>在做家具这件事上，英国设计师 Gavin Munro 想的不太一样：与其去种植树木然后砍下它们，为什么不让树木从一开始就长成特定的形状，直接变成可用的家具或是独一无二的艺术品呢？这个念头促成他创办了这个名为 Full Grown 的品牌，每一件产品都是通过模具的帮助直接由树木生长而成的。种植家具的方法更是免去了零件和胶水，如有需要他们会将树木嫁接在一起，也能保证牢固性。当然，要用上 Full Grown 的产品需要点耐心，一般需要四到五年的时间才能完成。因此，在家具之外，Munro 也在众筹活动中增加了类似图解书、T 恤、托特包一类的周边。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1118162081/full-grown-trees-grown-directly-into-art-and-furni\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，家具的价格从 450 英镑起，预计明年 12 月出货。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211444XgKHATfyGvqDNREr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.055882\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201701222114425lyT3RNesrB2caxz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707353\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211444zB51pdUDGZ0xOQ4W.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.657353\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211444YTVFKbLdjlmhXU9p.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211442Pnb87QCpVTkceaZv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.670588\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211442dEtG2Vcvm8CLBlRx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>SuperYR by Supergraph</h3><p>很多人都知道提前做好计划的重要性，但你还记得自己最后一次写计划是什么时候吗？来自美国洛杉矶的设计工作室 Supergraph 发现，这很有可能是因为现有的规划工具并不好用：虽然智能手机上的日历 app 起到了很好的提醒作用，但它们并不能满足做规划的需要。为此，他们推出了这款名为 SuperYR 的磁性白板大日历，长宽为 76*100 厘米。它分为正反两面，红色的一面是日程表，白色的一面则是日历，两面的每一格都是空白的，可以任意涂改。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/supergraph/superyr\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 29 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201701222115030OY8pMUtEGdFSrmR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211503hfSKx23TsPHrundI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201701222115034uDXTQcOKh1mVglp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211503bDe7cL1FusYv6Nfr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201701222115030JpdjUBfWEGiCyLD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211504eaELnHRB0JkUfDCv.png\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><h3>SprayPrinter</h3><p>想玩喷漆但画功差怎么办？来自美国的设计团队研发了一款可以帮你喷对地方的喷漆器 SprayPrinter，只要通过配套的 app，就能在任何物品的表面喷出你想要的图像。它的操作方式也并不困难：在 app 中设定好想要喷涂的画面，将手机对准预备喷涂的物体固定好之后，装上喷漆就能开工了。在喷涂的过程中，它会自动识别出喷涂位置，不用担心图像走形。这个相当智能的工具售价不菲，为 247 欧元，你可以通过<a href=\"http://sprayprinter.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211544ACDnO5HoE0tvw4dP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201701222115455hEyKjkdePtrH4gY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211546AfB9r4DaeJlEjoCw.gif\" data-ratio=\"0.411765\" data-format=\"gif\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211546vLxOHq8P2tQjc9mM.gif\" data-ratio=\"0.404167\" data-format=\"gif\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211544O1fKQEXG4cVRSi2F.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.202941\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Kiriki Press by Michelle Galletta</h3><p>几年前，当加拿大设计师 Michelle Galletta 为如何给自己的新侄女准备礼物而犯愁时，她找到了母亲的刺绣工具和一本古老的刺绣指南。在手忙脚乱地完成了三只猫头鹰娃娃后，她发现自己喜欢上了这一手工艺。经过多年的练习和设计，她在 Esty 上创立了自己的刺绣品牌 Kiriki Press，推出了一系列动物主题的 DIY 玩偶套装，让更多人能够通过这些可爱的小动物享受到刺绣的乐趣。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/kirikipress\" rel=\"nofollow\">网店链接</a>，售价从 18 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211742NJlYWrSxvTpewgOZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.486667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211741MRegcrhnu0P1UTx2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211742c17aYSP5Erle9HWs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211742nHfKlWaDYC2ORJXN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211741Omo6bGwLSDuMNRWP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Frigid Air by Guillaume Landin</h3><p>尽管市面上也有不少小型的冰箱，它的体积、重量对过着经常搬家或是想要开展户外活动的人来说，仍旧是绕不开的问题。设计师 Guillaume Landin 想到了将主机和储物空间分开的解决办法，设计了这台名为 Frigid Air 的冰箱。它的储物空间相当于一个柔软的白色大袋子，浅蓝色的内层采用防水织物打造，通过尼龙搭扣带和隔热材料制成的外层相连，可以随时拆卸，便于清洗。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211619LphwXBxFeVYzq08n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211619iG95VrfWLjYOpvsS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.065714\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211619wpLzvrXYt510bysU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211619BHyfhqb0EDvMJ49n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.785714\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Monstea Tea by Yvone Moser</h3><p>圆锥形的身体加上明亮的配色，这些名叫 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/34259285/Monstea-Tea-Packaging-for-Kids\" rel=\"nofollow\">Monstea</a> 的“怪兽”其实是德国设计师 Yvone Moser 专门为小朋友们设计的茶叶包装。这些面带微笑的“茶叶怪”的肚子上标记了对应的三种茶叶符号，相关的信息则藏在底部，对小朋友来说更加直观。它们的嘴巴刚好被设计成了开口，取出茶包之后还能用作花器种上花草——每一包茶叶中都藏有一个名为 magic tea 的茶包，可以当做种子的肥料使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211637PMLln1OZuUp58A0K.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.690625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211637UO7DkpbzLleCP2nh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.690625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211637ynYeBt6GvSuUsWVO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.690625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170122211637Snd9hCzX8bk61Meq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.690625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div>"}